metadata.name: Cottagecore Del Rey 1/1
metadata.description:
Part archive, part store. Glorious mix of treasures, tools with ambitions to be universal. Brooklyn antics, a cinematic atmosphere of old signs and store fronts, relics of mere needle and thread. Long sleeve knitted woolen sweater, heart-shaped neckline, high waisted front button up mini suede red skirt. 

Synth Graph: a center front view, close up portrait, 2012, photograph of a beautiful tanned female model wearing woolen maroon mini skirt with silver buttons and an oversized green collar shirt, red lipstick, walking down the streets of manhattan 1990s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 100, scale: 11.
